parameters: Chieftain: "My apologies... for gathering everyone at such a late hour..."
Villager A: "What's going on... at this time of night?"

Villager B: "Isn't it dangerous to gather like this? What if we're found
out?"
Villager C: "But if something happens, Lord Banka will take care of it."
Chieftain: "Sigh... Banka, huh... well then."
Villager A: "Ugh..."
Villager D: "Ah, my head..."
Villager E: "Nngh... what is this...?"
Chieftain: "I see... As expected of Iburu..."
Villager A: "Chieftain... what is this...?"
Villager B: "What in the world have we..."

Chieftain: "It seems you've all been under a long spell of hypnosis... you
were hypnotized..."
Villager C: "Hypnosis...?"
Villager D: "What the... it seems like we've made some terrible mistake..."

Chieftain: "That's right... The village was occupied by Chancellor Shif of
the kingdom, and all the heroic deeds of Kru, who saved the village, were
credited to Banka... And then Umi was taken as his concubine..."
Villager E: "What?!"
Villager F: "Umi-chan has?!"

Chieftain: "Yes... she must have been through hellish days. Being held
hostage and at their mercy..."
Villager A: "Damn it! What a disaster..."
Villager B: "I'm sorry... Umi-chan..."

Chieftain: "Yes... but I've reached my limit of patience... I'm thinking of
how to break this current situation..."
Villager C: "But... how do we..."
Chieftain: "...I'm considering using the curse of destruction..."
All Villagers: "What?!"
